query:
INSERT INTO healths(
                appointment_id,
                temperature,
                weight,
                upper_blood_pressure,
                lower_blood_pressure,
                heart_pulse,
                hemoglobin,
                is_good_health,
                note
            )
            VALUES(
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7,
                $8,
                $9
            )
            RETURNING id
